    "name": "KILL IT WITH FIRE! 2",
    "steam_appid": 2357000,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/69e0d251b7e34b67b19cab4efacd404a.poster.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/69e0d251b7e34b67b19cab4efacd404a.webm?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/69e0d251b7e34b67b19cab4efacd404a.mp4?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是灭杀者，你的使命是讨伐占领多元宇宙的蜘蛛大军。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人游戏，或与好友组成最多4人的小队进行在线合作，在剧情战役中大杀四方，让这些虫子看看谁才是老大。或者加入人类大战蜘蛛的疯狂PvP模式，欢笑不断，尖叫不止。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不论如何选择，有一件事是肯定的——是时候让蜘蛛燃烧了！！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/484f9ac193976089da7ca4297684dcb0.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/12b872f73b449b08d15b7d0c9076e35e.poster.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/12b872f73b449b08d15b7d0c9076e35e.webm?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/12b872f73b449b08d15b7d0c9076e35e.mp4?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >45种不负灭杀者威名的武器和物件可供挑选，用来对这些八条腿的怪物发动战争。报纸拍扁，火烧成灰，旋转机枪扫射，火箭发射器轰炸，激光剑劈砍……你的小队会用何种方式碾碎虫群？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/7779108e32c35c64db2648b1070a5702.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/19fad8b051775741df6b670772078bf9.poster.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/19fad8b051775741df6b670772078bf9.webm?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/19fad8b051775741df6b670772078bf9.mp4?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开启跨越七个独特世界的史诗级蜘蛛狩猎之旅。灭杀神秘庄园中的蛛形纲害虫，解放狂野西部的小镇，探索赛博空间，深入蜘蛛地狱。每个关卡都会带来独一无二的蜘蛛对战体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/6b7d196dc9c7453e165cb1d515694e89.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/0192d665e94195c3947a43c51dd76b41.poster.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=660 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/0192d665e94195c3947a43c51dd76b41.webm?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/0192d665e94195c3947a43c51dd76b41.mp4?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在咕嘟咕嘟的坩埚中炼制魔法药水。化身怪兽大小的狂人摧毁大都市。帮助仙人掌的酒馆抵御蜘蛛敌潮。在虚拟现实中赢下无人机竞赛。超过60项挑战等你来完成！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/22a971d4238302462920e026506d45b5.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/6109feb7a36c865245871c2742b45d97.poster.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/6109feb7a36c865245871c2742b45d97.webm?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/6109feb7a36c865245871c2742b45d97.mp4?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可能想问：“猎杀蜘蛛什么的听起来是很有意思啦，但如果我想要扮演蜘蛛呢？”没问题，在名为“蜘蛛狩猎”的8人在线PvP模式下，的确可以扮演蜘蛛，展开真正的人类与真正的蜘蛛（也由人类控制）之间的较量！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关键特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    7个蜘蛛肆虐的维度待你拯救</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    60多项独特的游戏内挑战供你完成</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    45种武器和其他物件可供解锁和制作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    全程可单人游玩或4人合作游玩的战役</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    由Miles Luna（代表作包括《RWBY》和《Red vs Blue》）操刀编写的闹剧情节</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    最多支持8名玩家的PvP多人模式“蜘蛛狩猎”</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    20多个小时的游玩内容，保证至少大笑3次</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    总计157亿在多元宇宙中等待灭杀的蜘蛛</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 简体中文, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 韩语, 俄语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
